$ Oracle: Cartesian join

A *cartesian join* joins two tables without having a condition to join them.

sa:

  Plan operation `→ development/databases/Oracle/SQL/statement/execution/plan/operations/merge-join/cartesian`

  → development/databases/Oracle/SQL/join/cross[cross join]

  Events:
    • 10076 enables cartesian product join costing
    • 10770 disables optimization to avoid buffering the right side of a cartesion join
